## Why This Is Asked
Tests practical integration of multiple configuration tools in a complex, real-world setup with security, drift, and rollback considerations.

## Key Concepts
- Idempotent secret rotation across CM tools
- Drift detection and automated remediation
- Canary testing and safe promotion
- Auditability and rollback strategies

## Code Example
```javascript
// Pseudo: trigger secret rotation for a service
async function rotateSecrets(service, vaultClient) {
  const newSecrets = await vaultClient.rotate(service);
  await pushToAgents(service, newSecrets);
  await reconcileWithPuppetChef(service, newSecrets);
}
```

